Freddie cross-project Rust gotchas. rs-plugkit exec utility verbs: binary advertises exec:status/exec:close/exec:sleep in hook help, but if the Cmd enum lacks variants, use exec:wait <secs> for waits and read task output via fs.readFileSync instead of exec:status. rs-exec timeout alias: both --timeout (long-form) and --timeout-ms (plugin convention) accepted on Cmd::Exec and Cmd::Bash.